original: Brise, Gustaf Ivan Alfred, tandläkare, Karlshamn, f. 17/6/92 i Mjölby. G. 22 m. tandl. Greta Bodekull. Barn: Hiansi f. 2;2, Sven 25, Margareta 30. — Stud :ex. i Jöniköping 10, ekon. ex. v. HHS 12, tandl :kand. 16, tandläkare 18. Tj :man i A-B Gbgs Bank i Sthlm 12-15, tandl :praktik i Karlshamn sed. 18. Ordf. i Blek. tandl :-fören. 31-33.
translated: Brise, Gustaf Ivan Alfred, dentist, Karlshamn, b. June 17, 1892 in Mjölby. Married in 1922 to dentist Greta Bodekull. Children: Hiansi b. 1922, Sven b. 1925, Margareta b. 1930. He obtained a degree in dentistry from Jönköping in 1910, an economics degree from HHS in 1912, a dental degree in 1916, and became a licensed dentist in 1918. He worked as a clerk for A-B Gbgs Bank in Stockholm from 1912-1915, and then established a dental practice in Karlshamn in 1918. He served as chairman of the Blekinge Dental Association from 1931-1933.
